==評價==
===間諜軟體醫生===
間諜軟體醫生獲得PC World雜誌第2007年10月號的''Best Buy''獎：「PC Tools間諜軟體醫生5.0是偵測和移除我們廣告和間諜軟體的贏家。」<ref>Naraine, Ryan. [http://www.pcworld.com/article/id,136191-page,1/article.html "PC Tools Spyware Doctor 5.0 Review"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/id,136191-page,1/article.html |date=20080702194854 }}, ''PC World'', 21 August 2007</ref>間諜軟體醫生也獲得了數個PC Magazine的Editor’s Choice獎<ref>Rubenking, Neil. [http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,1895,1829280,00.asp "Weeding out the spys - Editors' Choice: Spyware Doctor 3.2"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,1895,1829280,00.asp |date=20081221161655 }}, ''PC Magazine', June 19, 2005</ref>，包括間諜軟體醫生含防毒5.5（2008年）<ref>Rubenking, Neil. [http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2704,2251725,00.asp "Spyware Doctor with AntiVirus 5.5 - Editors' Choice Review"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2704,2251725,00.asp |date=20080725233152 }}, ''PC Magazine', 22 January 2008</ref>。此產品還獲得了其他世界各地的獎項。

並非所有的評價都是正面的。早期版本的間諜軟體醫生5.0（由Scratch改版而成），得到一些負面評價<ref>Vamosi, Robert. [http://www.cnn.com/2007/TECH/ptech/03/29/spyware.doctor/index.html "Nettlesome glitches sink Spyware Doctor 5"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnn.com/2007/TECH/ptech/03/29/spyware.doctor/index.html |date=20140911204102 }}, CNN, 29 March 2007</ref>。CNET的Download.com給間諜軟體醫生三顆星的評價[http://www.download.com/Spyware-Doctor/3000-8022_4-10293212.html?cdlPid=10795134 reviews]{{Wayback|url=http://www.download.com/Spyware-Doctor/3000-8022_4-10293212.html?cdlPid=10795134 |date=20080527064511 }}並評論說：「在我們的測試中，間諜軟體醫生反覆地把一些無害的cookie標示為潛在威脅，比起其它我們所測試的反間諜軟體都還來的多。我們也無從得到每個威脅被間諜軟體醫生標示的原因或詳細資訊。」

==批評==
華盛頓居民曾告賽門鐵克旗下的PC Tools登陸檔技師、效能工具箱（Performance Toolkits）、和[[諾頓電腦醫生|諾頓電腦醫生]]（Norton Utilities）進行假的掃描，以欺騙消費者付費購買該產品<ref>{{cite web|last=Yin|first=Sara|date=12 January 2012|title=Symantec Sued for Scareware Tactics|url=http://securitywatch.pcmag.com/none/292826-symantec-sued-for-scareware-tactics|publisher=[[PC_Magazine|PC Magazine]]|accessdate=22 January 2012|archive-date=2014-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101184923/http://securitywatch.pcmag.com/none/292826-symantec-sued-for-scareware-tactics|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該訴訟主訴諾頓公司蓄意執行假掃描，且其掃描結果為假<ref>{{cite web|last=Greenberg|first=Andy|date=11 January 2012|title=Lawsuit Claims Symantec "Scareware" Warns Of Fake Threats To Sell Upgrades|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/andygreenberg/2012/01/11/lawsuit-claims-symantec-scareware-warns-of-fake-threats-to-sell-upgrades/|publisher=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|accessdate=22 January 2012|archive-date=2014-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140911200557/http://www.forbes.com/sites/andygreenberg/2012/01/11/lawsuit-claims-symantec-scareware-warns-of-fake-threats-to-sell-upgrades/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。結果此訴訟賽門鐵克勝訴。

